#

Cajun Shrimp Burger

25 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishGluten (if using regular buns)

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodHigh ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Quick MealSpicyComfort Food

Description

A spicy, juicy shrimp burger bursting with Cajun flavors, served on a toasted bun with zesty toppings.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato (sliced): 1
  • green onion (chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • cajun seasoning: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
